this included mana burn.<br>
<br>
this was changed in a patch, stating that it was never intended to work this way.  it now doubles your unmodified base damage first. ie, (same as above) would hit normal for 1100, but only crit 2100 (not 2200). <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.angelfire.com/trek/fastboy21/yeli2.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
